name: PIX EGG - BETA EGG
description:
Welcome to PIX! 
Burn me to receive a generative 1/1 PIX in your wallet.

If you send $EVIL or $DARK tokens to address "sacrifice.tez" before burning, your next burned egg will be supercharged and receive special powers, traits and graphic effects.

Chances depend on the amount of token you send to sacrifice.tez
1.000 $EVIL or 1.000 $DARK will grant you 100% chance of receiving special traits.

EVIL and DARK traits are DIFFERENT. Try each one!

Don't worry, there's a little chance to receive ANY trait even if you don't sacrifice tokens.

Hatch process is manually triggered and may take up to 48 hours.

Check out every pix on https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/the_pix/

Follow @ThePIX_tez to get more informations about traits rarity and other crazy stuff!
